Availability.Beyond Faerûn:
* In the continent of [[Kara-Tur]], oranges were cultivated in the country of [[Shou Lung]], such as on the [[Shao Mountains]] around the [[Sumitra tower]], despite the harshness of that local climate. Within the town of [[Jade Gate Spring]], [[korobokuru]]s tended groves of both oranges and [[peach]]es.
* In the continent of [[Zakhara]], oranges were cultivated in the orchards of the fortress [[Sarahin]] and in the [[Garden of Delights]] within it.{{cite book/Assassin Mountain/Holy Slayer Sourcebook|28-29}}
* Off the coast of [[northwest Zakhara]], located within the [[Genie's Turban]] island chain, oranges grew on the [[Island of Gardens]].
